/-- The map `Œ©[A‚ÅÑR] ‚Üí‚Çó[A] Œ©[B‚ÅÑR]` given a square
A --‚Üí B
‚Üë     ‚Üë
|     |
R --‚Üí S -/
def kaehler_differential.map : Œ©[A‚ÅÑR] ‚Üí‚Çó[A] Œ©[B‚ÅÑS] :=
derivation.lift_kaehler_differential
  (((kaehler_differential.D S B).restrict_scalars R).comp_algebra_map A)

